    <string name="first_launch_tour_step1_title">Home: your budget</string>
    <string name="first_launch_tour_step1_body">The Home tab shows each category, spending versus its monthly target, and your overall month total. Tap a category to focus transactions, or use the icons to edit targets and add categories.</string>
    <string name="first_launch_tour_step2_title">Budget month</string>
    <string name="first_launch_tour_step2_body">Use the month control on Home to switch the budget period you are viewing. Your targets and totals follow the selected month.</string>
    <string name="first_launch_tour_step3_title">Transactions</string>
    <string name="first_launch_tour_step3_body">The Transactions tab lists everything that counts in your budget. Add a manual line when you paid cash, tap a row to edit details, assign categories, or create merchant rules so future SMS lines sort themselves.</string>
    <string name="first_launch_tour_step4_title">Settings</string>
    <string name="first_launch_tour_step4_body">Allow bank SMS (if you want automatic imports), run a one-time SMS import, set daily backups, tune when your budget month starts, and adjust categories for the current month.</string>
    <string name="first_launch_tour_step5_title">You are ready</string>
    <string name="first_launch_tour_step5_body">You can skip this tour anytime with Skip. Explore the bottom tabs whenever you need—happy budgeting.</string>
